  "title": "The Impact of the Internet on Daily Life",
  "transcript": "The internet has affected every aspect of my daily life from morning to evening. In the morning, I use the internet to check the weather forecast, read news, and go over my email inbox. While I study during the day, the internet provides valuable information about my school courses for me to study effectively. At night, I play computer games for a while, and chat with my family members and friends through an instant messenger. The internet maybe reduces the chance of face-to-face communication, but it shortens the distance between people far away from each other at the same time.",
